   known to influence prospective buyers. An emerging literature has
   started to look at how ratings are generated and, in particular, how
   they are influenced by prior ratings. We study the social influence of
   prior ratings and, in particular, investigate any differential impact of
   prior ratings by strangers ("crowd") versus friends. We find evidence of
